flowchart TD
    classDef store fill:#e1d5e7,stroke:#9673a6,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef layout fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef comp fill:#dae8fc,stroke:#6c8ebf,stroke-width:2px;

    Store[useTelemetryStore\nZustand]:::store

    Dashboard[Main Dashboard Layout]:::layout

    MapCard[Geospatial Pane\nReact-Leaflet]:::comp
    MapCard -->|Selector: GPS/Position| Store

    HudCards[Telemetry Cards Grid]:::comp
    HudCards -->|Selector: VFR/Battery/Sats| Store

    AttitudeInd[Attitude SVG Indicator]:::comp
    AttitudeInd -->|Selector: Roll/Pitch| Store

    CompassRose[Compass Heading SVG]:::comp
    CompassRose -->|Selector: Heading| Store

    Dashboard --> MapCard
    Dashboard --> HudCards
    Dashboard --> AttitudeInd
    Dashboard --> CompassRose
